Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:55.31,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,There aren't any statues \Nof Father outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:58.12,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,What if it's carrying the White Fang?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.65,Оригінал,Doc Klein,0,0,0,,The train will arrive momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:03.30,Оригінал,Doc Klein,0,0,0,,Will you give the order to open the gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.79,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,You carry a heavy responsibility, Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.40,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.40,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.77,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,The gate isn't opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.52,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Isn't that bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.78,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Open up, Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:31.16,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,You carry a heavy responsibility, Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:36.41,Оригінал,Doc Klein,0,0,0,,At this rate, the train \Nwill crash into the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.73,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Please, Weiss, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.08,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Ice Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.74,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:07.61,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Don't shut us out! Weiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.36,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.36,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.28,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.28,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.77,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:43.48,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Amazing! The walls keep opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:47.48,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Hah! This must be some \Nof that dream maintenance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:55.29,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.39,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,Whoa! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.78,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,What in the world is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.52,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,How far will it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.48,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Look at the next wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.50,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,The tracks are climbing upwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.53,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Go as far as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.94,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Is that like a station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.84,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,The walls are gone, \Nbut something new appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.07,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Guess the plan worked, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:23.03,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Your plan is up next, leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:24.66,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:43.57,Оригінал,Robot Soldiers,0,0,0,,Big Nicholas! Big Nicholas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:50.02,Оригінал,Robot Soldiers,0,0,0,,Big Nicholas! Big Nicholas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.16,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,We won't be thrown out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:00.01,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,All right, let's get started with my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.23,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Jaune, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.80,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.95,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,I'm cold and my nose feels itchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.75,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,My eyes are watery, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.41,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Having a bad reaction to the Nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:16.01,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,You're still the only one who can move \Naround freely. We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.62,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:24.01,Оригінал,Doc Klein,0,0,0,,Finally, finally we were able to \Nreceive a train, Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:30.02,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Blake defended the train \Nfrom the White Fang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:33.15,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Even Jaune... but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.65,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,You carry a heavy responsibility, Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.06,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Responsibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:43.05,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:44.26,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.95,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Where did those four go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.32,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,There's trouble, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:55.08,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,Blake took Ruby, Yang, and Jaune, \Nand they all rode the train inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:58.16,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Silence yourself! I was aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:03.00,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,Huh? Sister, are you trying \Nto let Faunus into the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.43,Оригінал,Willow,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:14.52,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,Are you truly worthy to be a child \Nof the Schnee family, Weiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:21.68,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Only I can uphold the Schnee family's pride \Nand carry out Big Nicholas's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:32.03,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Even if the train returns to the city, \Nthe city will not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.98,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,I will make Blake understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.73,Оригінал,Nora,0,0,0,,He looks really uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.23,Оригінал,Ren,0,0,0,,Good luck, Jaune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:03.61,Оригінал,Pyrrha,0,0,0,,Good luck, Jaune. I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.65,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Sniffle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.53,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Is he gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:15.65,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't breathe through \Nmy nose. I'm so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.29,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,I just want a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.42,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Huh? Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.49,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Ah... achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.92,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,He's being totally ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.87,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Wow, Jaune!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.78,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,I probably would've taken that as an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.52,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Hello, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.22,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Wha—!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.79,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Big Nicholas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.19,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,I'm Dopey Klein, one of the Seven Butlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:06.05,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,I'm guarding the Sillies here \Nto make sure they don't esca—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.26,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.95,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Weren't you a Silly, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:13.52,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to go outside, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.52,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,That's kind of annoying, \Ncoming from a bozo like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:27.26,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Would you mind opening up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:30.84,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,No way! I gotta keep the Sillies locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:35.36,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,But I'm one of them, right? \NIf you don't open up, I can't get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.33,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Are you a dummy or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.40,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.92,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.92,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:58.14,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Huh? Why can't I close?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.89,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.42,Оригінал,Ren,0,0,0,,Mew! Mew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.42,Оригінал,Nora,0,0,0,,Mew! Mew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.79,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Are those for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:20.02,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Ah, this helps! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:28.96,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,I came to let you guys out, but it's \Nreally warm and comfortable here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:32.52,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,My nose stopped \Nfeeling itchy, too. I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.82,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Isn't this Team RWBY's relic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.46,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Different color, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:03.37,Оригінал,Silly Weisses,0,0,0,,Tee hee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.38,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Oh! What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.31,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,I can't close! I can't close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:10.72,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,This is weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.49,Оригінал,Dopey Klein,0,0,0,,Wha—!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:15.30,Оригінал,Silly Weisses,0,0,0,,I wanna be free to go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.19,Оригінал,Silly Weisses,0,0,0,,I wanna go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.35,Оригінал,Silly Weisses,0,0,0,,I love festivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.59,Оригінал,Silly Weisses,0,0,0,,Gimme a compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:19.58,Оригінал,Silly Weisses,0,0,0,,I wanna be spoiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.59,Оригінал,Silly Weisses,0,0,0,,I wanna play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.51,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Is that... Weiss when she was little?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:27.01,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Did she keep her childhood \Nfeelings locked up all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:30.27,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Is that right, Weiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:33.10,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,It's from Jaune.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:35.34,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Hello? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.28,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Eh? A relic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.38,Оригінал,Commander Klein,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:50.83,Оригінал,Commander Klein,0,0,0,,As long as my eyes glow red, I, Grumpy \NKlein, will not let dummies run free!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.80,Оригінал,Commander Klein,0,0,0,,I wanna be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:02.31,Оригінал,Robot Soldier,0,0,0,,I wanna play outside with my buddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.44,Оригінал,Robot Soldier,0,0,0,,I wanna eat lots of sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.40,Оригінал,Jacques Statue,0,0,0,,I wanna have fun talking to my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:13.04,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Jaune!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.37,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Ruby. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:20.89,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,This time it's yellow. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.20,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,It feels like we're totally nailing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:26.71,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,All of that stuff happening is...\Nfine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.20,Оригінал,Robot Soldier,0,0,0,,I don't wanna mind my manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.20,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:29.78,Оригінал,Robot Soldier A,0,0,0,,I wanna play outside with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:33.71,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,The feelings she always kept bottled up \Nare free now. Isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.18,Оригінал,Robot Soldier B,0,0,0,,I wanna eat lots of sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.89,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Everyone wants to be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:40.47,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,You can't always keep the things \Nyou care about locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.50,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,They gotta be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.97,Оригінал,Ren,0,0,0,,Be free...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.60,Оригінал,Nora,0,0,0,,Be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.20,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Oh! They talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.55,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:53.02,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,You guys are the resistance. \NYou fight for freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:54.27,Оригінал,Ren,0,0,0,,We will fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.24,Оригінал,Nora,0,0,0,,We'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.13,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,For freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.13,Оригінал,Ren,0,0,0,,For freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.13,Оригінал,Nora,0,0,0,,For freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.13,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,For freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:17.38,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:22.17,Оригінал,Commander Klein,0,0,0,,I wanna be free! I wanna be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.72,Оригінал,Commander Klein,0,0,0,,I wanna be fr—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.74,Оригінал,Commander Klein,0,0,0,,Augh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:34.73,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! You carry a\Nsuper-heavy responsibility, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:39.00,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,There's no way you could say you're \Nworthy to be a Schnee now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.46,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,Ah! Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.05,Оригінал,Negative Weiss,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.66,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,We got this far coming straight through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:03.73,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,It looks like all the soldiers \Nwent to where Jaune is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:05.06,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.01,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.96,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,This time, we have to beat \Nthe Grimm and wake Weiss up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:33.79,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Ahh, my nose and eyes hurt. \NI can't keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:34.98,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.36,Оригінал,Jaune,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.42,Оригінал,Ren,0,0,0,,Let us fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:40.84,Оригінал,Nora,0,0,0,,For freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.86,Оригінал,Robot Soldier,0,0,0,,I wanna play! I wanna play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.22,Оригінал,Ren,0,0,0,,Let us fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.64,Оригінал,Nora,0,0,0,,For freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.43,Оригінал,Robot Soldier,0,0,0,,I wanna talk to all sorts of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:52.61,Оригінал,Robot Soldier,0,0,0,,I wanna go outside! I wanna go outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:58.13,Оригінал,Silly Weiss,0,0,0,,I wanna have fun! I wanna play all the time!
